The Glenn Beck Program - 07/29/13


Monday, July 29, 2013 10:17 AM



 A big Monday for Glenn who joins us from Salt Lake City.
  Senator Ted Cruz joins the program to talk about his current fights in congress
  and Michele Bachmann takes Glenn on in a debate about the NSA and their data mining and storage.
